no-debugger.description:
Description

This rule disallowsdebuggerstatements.

Example ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-debugger: "error"*/

function isTruthy(x) {
    debugger;
    return Boolean(x);
}

Example ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-debugger: "error"*/

function isTruthy(x) {
    return Boolean(x); // set a breakpoint at this line
}
